<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to EchoSwap</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        color: #0d6efd;
      }

      .message {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .user-info {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
        border-left: 4px solid #0d6efd;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #999;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #0d6efd;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }


      .logo {
        max-width: 150px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
         <img src="https://i.ibb.co/ynyPgj84/website-logo.png" alt="website-logo" border="0"> 
        <h1>Welcome, {{name}}!</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="message">
        <p>We're excited to have you on board with <strong>EchoSwap</strong>.</p>
        <p>Your account has been created successfully. You can now start posting products, chatting with others, and exchanging items in our trusted community.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="user-info">
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{name}}</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        <p><strong>Signup Date:</strong> {{signupDate}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions or need help, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>

      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display:inline-block; margin-top:20px; padding:10px 20px; background-color:#0d6efd; color:#fff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:5px;">Login to Your Account</a>


      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} EchoSwap. All rights reserved.<br />
        If you did not create this account, please <a href="{{supportUrl}}">contact us</a>.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
